Package io.github.acciochris

Class Level

java.lang.Object
io.github.acciochris.Level
public class Level extends Object
Level definition class. This defines the obstacles, the hole position, the initial ball position, the ball radius, as well as any relevant joints.
Version:
May 30, 2025
Author:
Chris Liu, Anvesh Pattaje
